1   Nepuonu Ilfarisayo o Sadukayo enetii aatem eyieu neitodol olmonekie ooing'uaa shumata. 
2  Newaliki ajoki, “Ore te nteipa nijojo, ‘Mesha ade taata amu kenyokie shumata.’ 
3  Nijojo tadekenya, ‘Keidis ade taata amu kenyokie shumata netunukua.’ Indimidimi intae aatumusu ilmonek le shumata kake mindimidimi aaibalie ilmonek le kuna katitin. 
4   Eing'oru kulo tung'ana torrok lena kata olmonekie kake meishori likae leme olapa le Yona.” Nelo aing'uaa ninche.

