13  Ore pee elo Yesu enkalo e Kaisari e Filipi neikilikuan ilooiteng'eni lenyena ajoki, “Kejo iltung'ana ae ng'ae Enkerai e Tung'ani?”


14   Nejoki, “Ejo kulikae Yohana Olaibatisani; nejo kulikae Eliya; nejo kulikae Yeremia, anaa obo loo loibonok le Nkai.”


15  Nejoki, “Paa aijojo intae kara nanu ng'ae?”


16   Newaliki Simon Petero ajoki, “Ira Iyie Kristo, Enkerai e Nkai naishu.”


17  Newaliki Yesu ajoki, “Imayiana Simon ara Yona, amu eitu kiboloki ena entoki naata osesen o sarge, kake Papa lai otii shumata. 
18  Naajoki nanu iyie, ira Petero naa te nchumata ena soit ashet enkanisa ai; nemegilu ae kata ltimito le nemeneng'a. 
19   Naa kaaisho iyie ilboleta le nkitoria e shumata ore eniyooki aen te nkop, neaku eidipaki aateen te shumata; ore enilak te nkop eidipaki aatalak te shumata.”


20  Neitanap ilooiteng'eni lenyena pee meliki oltung'ani nchere ninye Kristo.

